platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The app that lets you instantly eliminate extraneous elements like unsightly signs or random people in the background, with just a few swipes. It can even remove power lines and – incredibly – fences.

L’app qui vous permet d’éliminer instantanément des éléments superflus comme des panneaux ou des personnes en arrière-plan. Elle peut même effacer les câbles électriques et (croyez-le ou non) les clôtures.
このアプリを使えば、ほんの数回スワイプするだけで、看板や通行人といった不要な要素を画像から瞬時に削除できます。電線やフェンスなどのオブジェクトも削除して編集できます。
這個 App 可讓你只需輕掃幾下，即可清除無關元素，例如背景中難看的標誌或無關的路人，甚至可以移除電線和圍欄。

Photo editors don’t get much simpler than TouchRetouch, which lets you instantly eliminate extraneous elements (like trash cans, unsightly signs, or random people in the background) with a few swipes of the finger. It’s even got presets for automatically removing power lines and—incredibly—fences.
The app that lets you instantly eliminate extraneous elements like unsightly signs or random people in the background, with just a few swipes. It can even remove power lines and–incredibly–fences.
這款修圖 App 讓你只要滑幾下手指，就能立即移除背景中多餘的元素，如礙眼的標誌或路人。它甚至能移除電線和圍欄，且效果令人讚歎。
